servicedetails: Professional photography and video services use digital or film cameras to assist in staging and lighting the subject being photographed. These photographs and videos are used in company publications, instruction manuals, newsletters, or public relations. Professional photography and video services are sometimes digital or digitally enhanced and are similarly composed or shot. Resulting video footage is used for instruction, marketing, and other purposes.
